    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我理解为：客户端是圆形节点，FastAPI用矩形，Redis用圆柱形表示数据库，OpenAI也是矩形。连接关系上，客户端先到FastAPI，FastAPI去查Redis，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "client",
        "api",
        "redis"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Redis返回有两种情况：hit直接回FastAPI，miss的话要走OpenAI，拿到结果再存进Redis。最后FastAPI把响应返回给客户端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "redis",
        "api",
        "openai",
        "client",
        "hit",
        "miss"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出四个节点和基本连线：客户端→FastAPI→Redis，以及Redis命中时返回FastAPI的路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "client",
        "api",
