      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我看你画的Redis到OpenAI是双向箭头？应该是单向的，miss时从Redis指向OpenAI，然后OpenAI单独有一条线写回Redis，是两个单向箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "redis",
